caption.p: Effect of α-terpinene on D. melanogaster survival. Subtitles: Survival was analyzed at the indicated time points. Results are expressed as the Mean ± SD of the number of dead flies after each exposure time. a = p < 0.05 compared to the control, b = p < 0.05 compared to 1 mg/mL and c = p < 0.05 compared to 2 mg/mL.
